Package damageAnalysis

Class Summary
ContextModel Class for reading ContextModelData
DamageAnalysis Collection of methods for calculation of damage
DamageAnalysisContext Class, which holds the required InputData for a DamageAnalysis
DamageAnalysisFactory Class for creating a DamageAnalysisContext of a contextModel, a landuseDataModel, an administrationUnitModel (optional) and a waterlevelDataModel
DataModel Class for reading and writing ModelData like LanduseData, AdministrationUnitData and WaterlevelData
